    • externalCashTransferMC

      public double externalCashTransferMC
      It counts the inflow and outflow to this cash account from other accounts from other portfolios. It assumes that inflow and outflow happened always in the currency of this cash account. This way cash transfer between cash accounts with different currencies are not taken in account.
